{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5e1c6f8896","title":"关于对待土菲的政策问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a8fca6e383","index":0,"year":1938,"month":12,"day":9,"articleId":"5e1c6f8896"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"289a9d5d84","type":"paragraph","text":"关于对待土菲的政策问题的指示”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"5e1c6f8896"},{"id":"c6e52c93ed","type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年12月9日）对士雕政策应当是：1.我们武装与剩脏安民的责任，首先要恢复政权，委任或必换县长、区长，该复抗日秩序。2.在我们力量足够的地方择最坏的十非消灭之。3，收编较为弱而力量不大的土服部队，收编后，或争取之，或收枪解散之。4.对不能消灭、不能收编的土部队，则与之联络，准备实行前两项办法[1]这是毛泽东和王辣祥关于土匹政策问题致豫东游击支队彭雪枫电的主要内容。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"5e1c6f8896"}],"page":{"id":"7541a29867","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"5e1c6f8896","start":77,"end":77}}}},"__N_SSG":true}